opportunity to bring
security and stability and peace
to this region.

01:51.111 --> 01:55.315 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BENJAMIN NETANYAHU, Israeli
Prime Minister:
Israel's hand is extended to
peace in peace

01:55.348 --> 01:57.984 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
