02:25.512 --> 02:32.452 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BENJAMIN NETANYAHU: I want you
to know how
much we appreciate the change in
American

02:32.485 --> 02:34.187 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
