04:27.033 --> 04:35.108 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
This is a battle between
barbaric criminals
who seek to obliterate human
life and decent

04:35.141 --> 04:44.751 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
people, all in the name of
religion, people
