that Saudi Arabia
will adopt this path.

05:26.993 --> 05:31.531 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Like the Israelis,
the Saudis also
welcome the shift in the U.S.
approach to

05:31.564 --> 05:37.537 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
